x4freetext: Prepared by depositing specpure 59Co by a vacuum
evaporation technique on Al backing (~2 mg/cm2 thick).
The thickness of 59Co was lying between 37-187 ug/cm2.
Irradiated for 6 hours by ~60 nA beam current
an electron suppressed Faraday cup used
Two stacks consisting of 5 targets each of 59Co
backed by 2 mg/cm2 thick aluminum foils were used.
